The 2014 amendment,effective May 21, 2014, established fees for appraiser trainees and appraisal management companies; in Subsection A, in Paragraph (1), after "fee for", added "real estate appraiser trainee"; in Subsection A, in Paragraph (5), after "renewal fee", added "for a real estate appraiser trainee"; in Subsection A, in Paragraph (9), after "two hundred dollars ($200)", added "and an additional extension fee may be applied"; and added Subsection B.

